  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schi irr ta Dufeschana/ to Apſlehpfchanas Weetu.\natpuhtinajeet to Peekuſſuscho/\nun fchi irr ta Atſpirdſinaschana/\ntomehr tee ne grib to dfirdeht."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz wiakkeem ta KUN-\nGA Wahrds tahds buhs/ pa-\nwehli pawehledams/ pawehlt pa-\nwehledams/ gaidi gaididams/\ngaidi gaididams/ ſcheit maſſe-\nniht/ tur maſſeniht/ ka teem buhs\neet/ un atpakkat kriſt/ un fa-\ndausiteeſ/ un eetiſſiiteem un fa-\nguhſiiteem tapt."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tadeht klaufajt ta KUN-\nGA Wahrdu juhs Mehditaji/\njuhs Walditajt pahr tcheem Lau-\ndim/ kas Jeruſalemē irr."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo juhs fakkat: Mehſ ef-\nfam weenn Derribu ar to Nah-\nwi/ un weenn Saderrefchann ar\nto Ellt darriſchi/ jevitchu arri\ntahdas Bahtagas ka Pluhdi\nunhē/ tomehr tahs muhs ne\naiskems/ jo mehs eſtam Melkus\npar muhfu Pativerumu likku-\nſchi/ un appakſch tahs Wiltibas\neſtam mehs apſlehpufschees."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz fakka tas KUNGS\nKUNGSta: Redſ/ es eſmu\ntas/ kas eeſſch Ziangs weenu\nGruntes-Akminti leek/ weenu\npahrrandstu Akminti/ weenu\ndahrgu Stuhen-Akminti/ kas\ntabbi ſtipri dibbinahts/ kas tizz/\ntas ne behgs."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es eezelſchu to Teefu\npar Mehra-Aukti/ un to Taſſ-\nnibu par Swarru/ tad nodsſhe\nta Kruffa to Mello Patveru-\nma/ un Uhdens pahrpluhdihs"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un juhsfu Derriba ar ta-\nNahwes taps niḥzinata/ un ju-\nsu Saderrechana ar tahs Ell-\nne paſtahwehs. Kad tahs Pa-\ntagās ka Pluhdi nahk/ tad ta-\nfeet juhs no tahm ſainihti."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tai paſchā Laikā/ ka-\ntahs ateet/ tad tahs juhs u-\njems/ jo ikriht eet winnas zau-\nDeenā un Nakti. * Ka tikāt\nt\nApbehdinachana juhs mahza\nMahzihu welhra lift."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "So ta Gulta irr ihsa/\nne warr isſteeptees/ un taē Def-\nkis fchaurs/ ka appaffch ta n-\nwarr twertees."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tas KUNGS tapat\nzelfees ka us to Kalnu Prazim\nwiſsch tapatt duſmoſees ka Gi-\nbeona Eeleijā fawu Darbu dar-\nriht/ winna Darbs buhs tweſch\nun fawu Darrischann padarriht,\nwinna Darritchana buhs five-\nscha."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Nu tad/ ne apmehtijeet\niwairs/ ka juhtn Saitee ne tohp-\nzeertaks/ jo es eſnu weenu Iſ-\ndeldeschanu dsirdejs/ kam faws\nMehrs irr nolikts no ta Kiluga\nKUNGĀ Zebaoth puhr wiſju\nSemiti."
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Greeſeet ſchurp tahs Au-\ntis/ un klaufajt mannu Balti/\nrenumeet wehra/ un klaufajt\nmannu Runnaschann."
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Arrig weens Arrajs ik-\ndecuns ner? winſch fahrtu un\naprize"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
